vernac_cmds: Definition tl d := match d with | Nil => d | D0 d | D1 d | D2 d | D3 d | D4 d | D5 d | D6 d | D7 d | D8 d | D9 d => d end.

Fixpoint usize (d:uint) : nat := match d with | Nil => 0 | D0 d => S (usize d) | D1 d => S (usize d) | D2 d => S (usize d) | D3 d => S (usize d) | D4 d => S (usize d) | D5 d => S (usize d) | D6 d => S (usize d) | D7 d => S (usize d) | D8 d => S (usize d) | D9 d => S (usize d) end.
Fixpoint to_lu n := match n with | 0 => Decimal.zero | S n => Little.succ (to_lu n) end.

Fixpoint of_lu (d:uint) : nat := match d with | Nil => 0 | D0 d => 10 * of_lu d | D1 d => 1 + 10 * of_lu d | D2 d => 2 + 10 * of_lu d | D3 d => 3 + 10 * of_lu d | D4 d => 4 + 10 * of_lu d | D5 d => 5 + 10 * of_lu d | D6 d => 6 + 10 * of_lu d | D7 d => 7 + 10 * of_lu d | D8 d => 8 + 10 * of_lu d | D9 d => 9 + 10 * of_lu d end.
Lemma to_lu_succ n : to_lu (S n) = Little.succ (to_lu n).
Lemma to_little_uint_succ n d : Nat.to_little_uint n (Little.succ d) = Little.succ (Nat.to_little_uint n d).
revert d; induction n; simpl; trivial.
Lemma to_lu_equiv n : to_lu n = Nat.to_little_uint n zero.
Lemma to_uint_alt n : Nat.to_uint n = rev (to_lu n).
Lemma of_lu_eqn d : of_lu d = hd d + 10 * of_lu (tl d).
Ltac simpl_of_lu := match goal with | |- context [ of_lu (?f ?x) ] => rewrite (of_lu_eqn (f x)); simpl hd; simpl tl end.
Lemma of_lu_succ d : of_lu (Little.succ d) = S (of_lu d).
Lemma of_to_lu n : of_lu (to_lu n) = n.
Lemma of_lu_revapp d d' : of_lu (revapp d d') = of_lu (rev d) + of_lu d' * 10^usize d.

induction d; intro d'; simpl usize; [ simpl; now rewrite Nat.mul_1_r | .. ]; unfold rev; simpl revapp; rewrite 2 IHd; rewrite <- Nat.add_assoc; f_equal; simpl_of_lu; simpl of_lu; rewrite Nat.pow_succ_r'; ring.
Lemma of_uint_acc_spec n d : Nat.of_uint_acc d n = of_lu (rev d) + n * 10^usize d.

induction d; intros; simpl Nat.of_uint_acc; rewrite ?Nat.tail_mul_spec, ?IHd; simpl rev; simpl usize; rewrite ?Nat.pow_succ_r'; [ simpl; now rewrite Nat.mul_1_r | .. ]; unfold rev at 2; simpl revapp; rewrite of_lu_revapp; simpl of_lu; ring.
Lemma of_uint_alt d : Nat.of_uint d = of_lu (rev d).
Lemma to_lu_tenfold n : n<>0 -> to_lu (10 * n) = D0 (to_lu n).
Lemma of_lu_0 d : of_lu d = 0 <-> nztail d = Nil.
induction d; try simpl_of_lu; try easy.
Lemma to_of_lu_tenfold d : to_lu (of_lu d) = lnorm d -> to_lu (10 * of_lu d) = lnorm (D0 d).
Lemma to_of_lu d : to_lu (of_lu d) = lnorm d.
induction d; [ reflexivity | .. ]; simpl_of_lu; rewrite ?Nat.add_succ_l, Nat.add_0_l, ?to_lu_succ, to_of_lu_tenfold by assumption; unfold lnorm; simpl; now destruct nztail.
Lemma to_of (d:uint) : Nat.to_uint (Nat.of_uint d) = unorm d.
Lemma to_uint_inj n n' : Nat.to_uint n = Nat.to_uint n' -> n = n'.
Lemma to_uint_surj d : exists n, Nat.to_uint n = unorm d.
Lemma of_uint_norm d : Nat.of_uint (unorm d) = Nat.of_uint d.
Lemma of_inj d d' : Nat.of_uint d = Nat.of_uint d' -> unorm d = unorm d'.
Lemma of_iff d d' : Nat.of_uint d = Nat.of_uint d' <-> unorm d = unorm d'.
Lemma of_to (n:nat) : Nat.of_int (Nat.to_int n) = Some n.
Lemma to_of (d:int)(n:nat) : Nat.of_int d = Some n -> Nat.to_int n = norm d.
Lemma to_int_inj n n' : Nat.to_int n = Nat.to_int n' -> n = n'.
Lemma to_int_pos_surj d : exists n, Nat.to_int n = norm (Pos d).
Lemma of_int_norm d : Nat.of_int (norm d) = Nat.of_int d.
Lemma of_inj_pos d d' : Nat.of_int (Pos d) = Nat.of_int (Pos d') -> unorm d = unorm d'.

command: revert d; induction n; simpl; trivial.

induction d; intro d'; simpl usize; [ simpl; now rewrite Nat.mul_1_r | .. ]; unfold rev; simpl revapp; rewrite 2 IHd; rewrite <- Nat.add_assoc; f_equal; simpl_of_lu; simpl of_lu; rewrite Nat.pow_succ_r'; ring.

induction d; intros; simpl Nat.of_uint_acc; rewrite ?Nat.tail_mul_spec, ?IHd; simpl rev; simpl usize; rewrite ?Nat.pow_succ_r'; [ simpl; now rewrite Nat.mul_1_r | .. ]; unfold rev at 2; simpl revapp; rewrite of_lu_revapp; simpl of_lu; ring.
induction d; try simpl_of_lu; try easy.
induction d; [ reflexivity | .. ]; simpl_of_lu; rewrite ?Nat.add_succ_l, Nat.add_0_l, ?to_lu_succ, to_of_lu_tenfold by assumption; unfold lnorm; simpl; now destruct nztail.
